<link href="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=1517&amp;p=1619#p1619"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Hadith &amp; its Sciences • Praising Allāh whilst eating and drinking]]></title>

<category term="Hadith &amp; its Sciences" scheme="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewforum.php?f=7" label="Hadith &amp; its Sciences"/>
<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=1517&amp;p=1619#p1619"><![CDATA[
قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ:<br /><br />إن الله يرضى عن العبد أن يأكل الأكلة فيحمده عليها، ويشرب الشَّربة فيحمده عليها<br /><br />رواه مسلم ٢٧٣٤<br /><br />صحيح الجامع ١٨١٦ | الشيخ الألباني رحمه الله | صحيح<br /><br />The Messenger of Allāh صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ said:<br /><br />“Allāh is pleased with His slave when he eats something and praises Him for it, and when he drinks something and praises Him for it.”<br /><br />Narrated by Muslim, 2734.<br /><br />Saheeh al-Jāmi' 1816 | Shaykh al-Albāni رحمه الله | Saheeh <br /><br />Translated by Authentic Quotes on Facebook...<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=63">Abu Faatimah</a> — Tue Aug 15, 2017 10:16 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
