The Messenger of Allāh صلى الله عليه وسلم said:<br /><br />The most hated speech to Allāh is when a man says to another man: ‘Fear Allāh!’ and he replies, ‘Worry about your own self!’ “<br /><br />Shaykh al-Albāni Authenticated it in as-Saheehah 2598<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=63">Abu Faatimah</a> — Sun Mar 05, 2017 1:39 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
