<title type="html"><![CDATA[Hadith &amp; its Sciences • “Marry so that...]]></title>

<category term="Hadith &amp; its Sciences" scheme="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewforum.php?f=7" label="Hadith &amp; its Sciences"/>
<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=1226&amp;p=1292#p1292"><![CDATA[
The Messenger of Allāh صلى الله عليه وسلم said:<br /><br />“Marry so that (on the Day of Judgement) I will be delighted by your outnumbering <br />other nations. Do not practice monasticism like the Christians.”<br /><br />Shaykh al-Albāni authenticated it in as-Saheehah 1782<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=63">Abu Faatimah</a> — Sun Mar 05, 2017 1:38 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
