Shaykh Muhammad Sālih al-Uthaymeen said:<br /><br />I do not know of there being anything wrong with a shoe being upside down. But this is a very serious matter for some people. It may be very serious for some people but there is no basis for it. <br /><br />Nūr alad-Darb 15/65 <p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=63">Abu Faatimah</a> — Sun Mar 05, 2017 1:28 am</p><hr />
